Using standard normal distribution:
- \(P(Z \leq 0.5001) \approx 0.6915\)
- \(P(Z \leq -1.5003) \approx 0.0668\)
- \(P(-1.5003 \leq Z \leq 0.5001) = 0.6915 - 0.0668 = 0.6247\)

